dct_title_s: Æthiopia Inferior, vel exterior : partes magis septentrionales, quæ hic desiderantur, vide in tabula Æthiopiæ Superioris. Recto
dct_description_sm: Scale approximately 1:8,750,000 ; Relief shown pictorially ; Includes decorative title cartouche with natives and local fauna ; Map interior depicts several elephants and goats ; Covers Southern Africa from S 10⁰ southward, including southwestern Madagascar ; Amsterdam : J. Jansson
dct_rights_sm: The images on this web site, from maps in the collection of the Melville J.
